# RCoder HTTP API 测试脚本
# 用于手动测试 /chat 服务

### 创建新会话的请求
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "test_user",
  "prompt": "Hello, 请帮我创建一个简单的 Rust 项目",
  "agent_type": "codex"
}

###

### 使用现有会话发送请求
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "test_user",
  "prompt": "现在请帮我添加一个 Cargo.toml 文件",
  "session_id": "test_session_001",
  "agent_type": "codex"
}

### 使用特定 project_id 的请求
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "test_user",
  "prompt": "创建一个 Python 项目",
  "project_id": "python_project_123",
  "agent_type": "codex"
}

### 带有完整会话信息的请求
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "developer_user",
  "prompt": "帮我分析这个 Rust 代码的性能问题",
  "session_id": "rust_analysis_session",
  "project_id": "rust_performance_project",
  "agent_type": "codex"
}

### 测试会话重用（相同的 session_id）
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "developer_user",
  "prompt": "现在请帮我优化之前分析的代码",
  "session_id": "rust_analysis_session",
  "agent_type": "codex"
}

### 测试不同的项目类型
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "frontend_user",
  "prompt": "创建一个 React 组件来显示用户列表",
  "project_id": "react_frontend_project",
  "agent_type": "codex"
}

### 测试简单的代码生成请求
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "backend_user",
  "prompt": "帮我写一个简单的 Express.js 服务器",
